fitness.title: Motorized Treadmill AF-515
fitness.description: Workout from the comfort of your home with AF 515 Motorized Treadmill. Equipped with a powerful and noiseless 2.0 HP motor (4.0 peak) and a high-density 2-ply urethane belt, AF515 is a great option for beginners and fitness enthusiasts to crush your fitness goals.

fitness.description: Train harder with the new AF 517 Motorized Treadmill (N.S.). Featuring 15 pre-set smart workout programs and a 5HP motor (peak), the T-501 will keep you motivated to push harder.

fitness.title: Auto Inclination Treadmill TM-33
fitness.description: Engage in a whole new fitness experience with Treadmill TM 33 Built with a powerful 1.5/3.0 HP DC motor and an automatic motorized incline, TM-33 can deliver high-intensity training for walkers, runners and fitness enthusiasts. With the added benefit of elastomer cushion and intelligent space-saving design, make fitness a way of life.

fitness.title: Cross Trainer With Seat
fitness.description: Using a cross-trainer can deliver an instinctively natural stride by ensuring a safe and consistent strengthening workout for your upper and lower body with reduced stress on your knees. This cross trainer makes for an ideal fitness companion for your everyday workouts with an 8-level manual resistance control and additional personalization for your training sessions with heart-rate monitoring.

fitness.title: Cross Trainer EH-400
fitness.description: Powermax EH-400 Elliptical Cross Trainer delivers an instinctively natural stride with its patented front-drive design and electromagnetic 8-level resistance control ensuring safe and consistent strengthening workouts for your upper and lower body. The two-way ribbed drive system and pulse pads provide additional personalization for your workouts, making it an ideal fitness companion.

fitness.title: Cross Trainer C-500
fitness.description: The C-500 cross-trainer delivers an instinctively natural stride that ensures a safe and consistent strengthening workout for your upper and lower body with reduced stress on your knees. The 8-level resistance control provides additional personalization for your workouts with heart-rate monitoring, making it an ideal fitness companion for your everyday workouts.

fitness.description: Built to keep you fit, the Cockatoo CUB-01 is a modern exercise bike that comes with 8-level magnetic resistance to ensure uniform pressure across each weight level. The engineered seat structure allows the body to conform precisely to the desired posture, enabling maximum workout effect and helping you shed those extra K's

Whether you’re looking to improve your weight-loss targets or get toned, VP-500 is the perfect home fitness solution to maximize your fitness regime.
